    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Arcade Empire Tycoon</strong>, step into the shoes of an arcade owner and build your dream entertainment empire! Design and customize your arcade layout, choosing from a variety of machines, including claw machines, air hockey, basketball games, and more. Every machine adds its unique twist, offering a fun experience for your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your business wisely by setting ticket prices and balancing income from tickets, vending machines, and prizes. Hire and manage employees, such as attendants and mechanics, ensuring smooth operations and timely repairs. With each passing day, monitor your finances, track expenses like salaries and marketing, and invest in research to unlock new technologies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299460/extras/cf7eb5fdc9c2b04a2b9677391220aef0.poster.avif?t=1765219610\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299460/extras/cf7eb5fdc9c2b04a2b9677391220aef0.webm?t=1765219610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299460/extras/cf7eb5fdc9c2b04a2b9677391220aef0.mp4?t=1765219610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on marketing campaigns to boost your arcade's popularity, from flyer distribution to TV commercials. And as your business thrives, watch your arcade grow into a bustling hub filled with fun and excitement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299460/extras/9e9b9c1a716a30ead6c98dca01c419cd.poster.avif?t=1765219610\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299460/extras/9e9b9c1a716a30ead6c98dca01c419cd.webm?t=1765219610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299460/extras/9e9b9c1a716a30ead6c98dca01c419cd.mp4?t=1765219610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a deep progression system that includes unlocking new machines and mastering your financial strategy, <strong>Arcade Empire Tycoon</strong> offers endless entertainment for anyone looking to create their very own arcade empire!</p>",
